Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.01,OP6,,0,0,0,,OP Start
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.60,0:00:16.00,OP6,,0,0,0,,Hey boys, listen up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.00,0:00:20.60,OP6,,0,0,0,,Humans aren't such a big deal
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.31,0:00:25.44,OP6,,0,0,0,,Who needs tomorrow anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.44,0:00:28.71,OP6,,0,0,0,,so don't hide your fists
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.65,0:00:32.92,OP6,,0,0,0,,You're not old enough
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.92,0:00:39.29,OP6,,0,0,0,,to sell your dreams away to uncertainty
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.23,0:00:44.66,OP6,,0,0,0,,Hey boys, you're the only ones
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.66,0:00:48.26,OP6,,0,0,0,,who can pull the trigger in your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.70,0:00:51.64,OP6,,0,0,0,,All the kids said
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.64,0:00:54.64,OP6,,0,0,0,,We're living in this senseless, ridiculous,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.64,0:00:59.01,OP6,,0,0,0,,awesome world right at this moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.21,0:01:01.48,OP6,,0,0,0,,All the kids said
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.48,0:01:07.35,OP6,,0,0,0,,Don't forget every truth or lie
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.76,0:01:11.08,OP6,,0,0,0,,All the kids said
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.08,0:01:13.42,OP6,,0,0,0,,We're way too young to die
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.42,0:01:18.29,OP6,,0,0,0,,In this empty town lined with empty faces
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.29,0:01:20.56,OP6,,0,0,0,,All the kids took off
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.56,0:01:23.10,OP6,,0,0,0,,into this windless night
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.10,0:01:29.00,OP6,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,3000)}Because they want to change something
Comment: 0,0:01:31.04,0:01:31.07,OP6,,0,0,0,,OP End
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.40,0:01:36.90,Sign_1,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\bord3\fad(600,600)\pos(700,548)}The Promise That\N Could Not Be Kept
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.78,0:01:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Kakashi Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.56,0:01:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Sasuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.24,0:01:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Kakashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.41,0:02:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,How is Uzumaki Naruto's condition?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.49,0:02:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,He's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.20,0:02:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What about Sasuke?\NWhere's Uchiha Sasuke?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.64,0:02:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,How are the other Genin?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.74,0:02:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! By Lady Hokage's order,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.27,0:02:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,the first and second medical corps\Nhave been dispatched...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.59,0:02:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The wounded from all areas have\Nalready been gathered.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.37,0:02:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,They were convoyed after\Nadministering emergency treatment.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.25,0:02:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,How are their conditions?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.49,0:02:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Nara Shikamaru has minor injuries...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.55,0:02:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Inuzuka Kiba has serious injuries,\Nbut it's not life-threatening.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.58,0:02:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyuga Neji and Akimichi Choji\Nare in serious condition...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.10,0:02:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,At this point,\Nthere's no telling what will happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.89,0:03:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.20,0:03:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The ingredients and\Neffects of the medicine
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.58,0:03:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,have been thoroughly researched.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.58,0:03:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Excellent...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.09,0:03:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Now bring the deer antler!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.86,0:03:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.76,0:03:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,How is he... Big Sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.19,0:03:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,No walks for him for quite a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.31,0:03:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The muscles of his limbs\Nhave been severely damaged.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.66,0:04:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a vet, right, Big Sister?\NCan't you somehow...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.40,0:04:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.80,0:04:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll take time. But there's no threat\Nto his life, so rest easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.39,0:04:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Walks for you are out of the question\Nfor quite a while, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.00,0:04:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.22,0:04:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll soon be three hours...\NPlease take over.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.74,0:04:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.77,0:04:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Although we're making\Nthis kid's hair into a conductor,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.94,0:04:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,please don't mistake the cellular rate\Nof the deficient parts!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.38,0:04:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.36,0:04:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,As for the Chakra control, handle it\Nas if we're threading a needle!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.21,0:04:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.43,0:05:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no point in\Nyou getting frustrated, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.44,0:05:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Missions come with sacrifice...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.99,0:05:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You took the mental training, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.36,0:05:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Training and actual battle\Nare different, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.46,0:05:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I know what missions are about...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.86,0:05:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And I thought I knew what\Nthe Shinobi world is like.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.37,0:05:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I became a platoon leader\Nfor the first time on this mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.55,0:05:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,With that, I understood...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.21,0:05:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not cut out to be a Shinobi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.24,0:05:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Surprisingly fragile... for a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.60,0:05:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,This time...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.06,0:05:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The only thing I was able to do\Nas platoon leader...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.60,0:06:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,was to believe in everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.98,0:06:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I was naive...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.83,0:06:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't have enough power...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.53,0:06:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all my fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.37,0:06:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you afraid of getting hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.46,0:06:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Shikamaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.61,0:06:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to be argued down\Nby a girl and run away?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.10,0:06:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a drag...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.56,0:06:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to have arguments.\NI'm not a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.54,0:06:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... But you're not a man, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.52,0:06:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just a coward!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.61,0:06:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you quit being Shinobi,\Nthe missions will continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.86,0:06:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone has to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.95,0:06:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Your comrades will just\Nbe dispatched again...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.37,0:06:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,under a different platoon leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.81,0:07:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And your comrades might die there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.26,0:07:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But if at that time,\Nyou were the platoon leader...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.75,0:07:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,your comrades might be saved\Nfrom that happening to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.84,0:07:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,If you reflect on this time,\Nmake use of the experience and learn,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.59,0:07:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,you might be able to carry out missions\Nwith more perfection.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.29,0:07:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,If you really think your comrades\Nare important to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.52,0:07:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,before you think about running away...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.00,0:07:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,think about becoming more exceptional\Nfor the sake of your comrades!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.61,0:07:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what real comrades are,\Nyou coward!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.55,0:07:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,He's okay, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.81,0:08:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The antidote has stopped\Nthe death of cells
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.14,0:08:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,caused by the side effects of the Pills.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.15,0:08:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You were a big help this time, Shikaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.36,0:08:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The Nara Clan's secret medicinal\Npreparation manual was very useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.82,0:08:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It must've been tough to\Nmake something like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.28,0:08:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the result of day-to-day study.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.08,0:08:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.66,0:08:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Tsunade!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.92,0:08:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyuga Neji...\NHis safety line has been secured.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.43,0:08:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And, there's some information...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.02,0:08:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hatake Kakashi and Uzumaki Naruto\Nhave just now returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.18,0:08:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Although seriously injured,\Nit seems it's not life-threatening.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.62,0:08:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Two, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.45,0:09:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Shikamaru...\NIt seems the mission is a failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.92,0:09:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But, everyone is alive!\NThat's the most important thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.51,0:09:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time for sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.35,0:09:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll carry out the mission perfectly!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.74,0:09:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke... You're the chosen one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.74,0:09:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever... Just give me power.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.75,0:09:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though the form is different,\Nit's still Lord Orochimaru before your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.80,0:09:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't want to die,\Nuse more care in how you talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.47,0:10:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What? This intense Chakra...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.20,0:10:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... My future is inside this kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.66,0:10:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to where Orochimaru is!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.08,0:10:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Please...bring back Sasuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.22,0:10:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll bring Sasuke back without fail! I promise that on my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.68,0:10:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... You were awake, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.64,0:10:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Shikamaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.28,0:10:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going on ahead to Choji!\NWhat about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.28,0:11:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going on ahead to...\NNaruto and Sasuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.48,0:11:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... So everyone's okay.\NThat's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.63,0:11:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, Sasuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.76,0:11:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... he's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.98,0:11:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I still can't see him...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.07,0:11:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... But Lady Tsunade said that\Nhe should regain consciousness soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.95,0:11:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.16,0:11:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really a great help that
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.00,0:11:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Tsunade returned\Nto the Leaf Village.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.67,0:11:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,If she hadn't, right about now,\NChoji would be...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.26,0:12:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The Lady Fifth...Hokage.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.65,0:12:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You've come to visit?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.40,0:12:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Information sure travels fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.87,0:12:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakura...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.45,0:12:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.92,0:12:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard you suffered\Nquite a serious injury...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.04,0:12:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But you look well, considering.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.88,0:12:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry... Sakura...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.72,0:12:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you apologize?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.48,0:13:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Being you, you probably\Ngot reckless again, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.11,0:13:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez, you look like a mummy...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.07,0:13:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.10,0:13:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey... The weather's nice today.\NSo open the curtains.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.58,0:13:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakura! I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.52,0:13:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll keep my promise, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.48,0:13:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I promised on my life.\NThat's what I said, so I...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.64,0:13:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay already, Naruto...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.10,0:13:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakura! He...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.64,0:13:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I always...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.90,0:13:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,said that, so... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.07,0:13:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I stick straight to what I say!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.57,0:13:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my Way of Ninja!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.09,0:14:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.26,0:14:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Naruto...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.73,0:14:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get right to healing this injury \Nand I've got to bring Sasuke back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.05,0:14:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.70,0:14:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Per... Pervy Sage?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.83,0:14:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.71,0:14:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I've come today to tell you\Nsomething important.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.75,0:14:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,From here on,\Nas my official disciple,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.97,0:14:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll train you to become\Na full fledged Shinobi in three years.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.30,0:14:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Three years...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.39,0:14:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I've received some credible information\Nfrom a certain source
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.43,0:14:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,concerning the Akatsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.00,0:14:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Akatsuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.77,0:15:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems that it will be\Nthree or four years
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.52,0:15:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,before they come after you next.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.78,0:15:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.57,0:15:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Talking about stuff that's\Nso far down the road...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.70,0:15:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have the time\Nto be doing slowpoke training!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.41,0:15:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.54,0:15:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,If I don't go after\NSasuke immediately,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.21,0:15:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,he might be killed by Orochimaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.67,0:15:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,"Immortal" doesn't mean that \N the flesh is being maintained as is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.64,0:15:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Before his body decays,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.64,0:15:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,a strong and new flesh will be made \N into a vessel for his soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.19,0:15:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems you've learned\Nof the true purpose
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.15,0:15:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,for Orochimaru seeking Sasuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.44,0:15:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! Then that means you also knew?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.11,0:15:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I was looking into\NOrochimaru's Immortality Jutsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.00,0:15:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems with that Jutsu,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.66,0:16:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,he can't reincarnate into\Nthe next body for three years.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.74,0:16:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And unable to wait for Sasuke,\Nhe just recently reincarnated...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.90,0:16:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be okay for three years from now...\NThere is time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.26,0:16:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not a lie, is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.26,0:16:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a lie, is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.93,0:16:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.98,0:16:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.74,0:16:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget about Sasuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.57,0:16:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke went to Orochimaru\Non his own accord.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.17,0:16:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what you do,\Nhe won't change.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.92,0:16:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I've seen many Shinobi, so I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.59,0:16:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke is the same kind\Nas Orochimaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.30,0:16:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're thinking about bringing him back,\Njust forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.34,0:17:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That's something an arrogant fool\Nwould do!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.72,0:17:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,He may be nothing to you\Nbut he's my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.67,0:17:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Would a friend hurt his comrade?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.23,0:17:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a look at your current plight!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.66,0:17:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.41,0:17:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? Why would you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.92,0:17:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We were called Sannin together...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.59,0:17:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Weren't we comrades\Nsince we were kids?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.34,0:17:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,In every regard,\Nyou're a foolish guy, Jiraiya...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.76,0:17:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You lack thought\Nin everything you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.49,0:17:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why you didn't notice\Nwhat I was doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.29,0:17:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you rethink it, Orochimaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.74,0:17:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Absurd!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.15,0:17:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you be so stupid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.32,0:17:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how much I wanted it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.84,0:18:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,in the end, there was no way \N he would come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.21,0:18:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,After the agony, all that's left was\Nmy own powerlessness and regret.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.67,0:18:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want you to go through\Nthe same thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.88,0:18:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're going to go after Sasuke,\Nthen there'll be no training.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.51,0:18:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get Anbu Black Ops to watch you
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.60,0:18:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and depending on the case,\Nprohibit you from leaving the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.81,0:18:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not just an ordinary kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.48,0:18:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You possess the Nine Tail Fox.\NThat the Akatsuki is after!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.48,0:18:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,This is serious.\NI'll just have to do that...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.94,0:18:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,if you're going to act on your own\Nwithout listening to what I say.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.66,0:18:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Eventually, you're going to have to deal
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.04,0:18:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,with guys more troublesome\Nthan Orochimaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.25,0:18:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Give up on Sasuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.71,0:18:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Sooner or later this was\Ngoing to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.61,0:18:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't suffer anymore!\NForget and dismiss him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.01,0:19:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not just Jutsu or power...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.80,0:19:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're a Shinobi, develop eyes that\Ncan make the right judgment.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.27,0:19:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you're going to live\Nas a Shinobi, become wise.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.81,0:19:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,If you remain a fool...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.61,0:19:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,the reality is that it will be tough\Nliving in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.65,0:19:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.07,0:19:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's what being wise is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.95,0:19:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'm fine being a fool for life!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.12,0:19:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if by myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.29,0:19:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll create even more awesome Jutsu\Nand save Sasuke no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.38,0:19:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And, and,\NI'll even kick the Akatsuki's butt!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.35,0:19:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,If someone like you\Nwere to do it alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.44,0:19:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,the best you'd be able\Nto come up with
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.15,0:20:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,would be some\Nstupid erotic Jutsu, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.03,0:20:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It might somehow work out
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.70,0:20:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,if you are a big fool and\Nnot an ordinary fool...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.80,0:20:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Be prepared once\Nyou're out of the hospital,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.83,0:20:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,you big fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.17,0:20:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,See you then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.92,0:20:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.43,0:20:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,- It's been seven years since...\N...all the members gathered like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.89,0:20:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Since Orochimaru left\Nthe organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.20,0:20:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That Orochimaru has gotten\Nthe Sharingan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.86,0:20:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Itachi... Your little brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.53,0:20:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get hasty. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.49,0:20:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll kill Orochimaru eventually...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.25,0:20:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,More importantly,\Nthere are only three years left.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.01,0:20:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Can everyone accomplish\Nthe work required of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.66,0:20:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.84,0:21:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, our goal is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.74,0:21:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,to get everything,\Nincluding the Nine Tail Fox in question!
Comment: 0,0:21:08.10,0:21:08.14,ED9,,0,0,0,,ED Start
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.60,0:21:18.43,ED9,,0,0,0,,{\blur8}When I recalled the parts one by one,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.43,0:21:24.80,ED9,,0,0,0,,{\blur8}I felt as though I had understood everything
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.80,0:21:35.37,ED9,,0,0,0,,{\blur8}Faded words which I kept so close to me
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.68,0:21:45.15,ED9,,0,0,0,,{\blur8}Speechless nights, a hint of warmth,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.90,0:21:51.89,ED9,,0,0,0,,{\blur8}and this distant yearning for you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.20,0:22:01.20,ED9,,0,0,0,,{\blur8}I live, simply repeating this cycle
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.38,0:22:12.91,ED9,,0,0,0,,{\blur8}Held in my two hands is a droplet of time
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.36,0:22:23.36,ED9,,0,0,0,,{\blur8}Softly clutching forgotten memories, lost words
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.24,0:22:37.16,ED9,,0,0,0,,{\blur8}{\fad(0,2500)}I'll keep these thoughts...
Comment: 0,0:22:38.07,0:22:38.10,ED9,,0,0,0,,ED End
